{"tid":850312,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家樂火鍋完全屌打大快活","createTime":"2018-10-06T11:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T01:44:43.000Z","uid":167437,"like":10,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"80f9792a3e90f61a3b458f0a256dbdec6836c705","tid":850312,"uid":167437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"最近食左呢兩間各自既火鍋<br />\n大家樂肥牛 菜 烏冬<br />\n係你order完先係雪櫃拎出黎<br />\n大快活一食就食得出d肥牛係擺左出黎好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大快活d菜係非常多黑斑<br />\n大家樂就正正常常<br />\n<br />\n大快活個爐等5分鐘先滾<br />\n大家樂2 3分鐘就滾<br />\n<br />\n8安士牛 大快活仲要貴過大家樂4蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係多杯垃圾野飲<br />\n<br />\n大快活唯一可取之處就係d呀姐有禮貌d<br />\n其他真係狗也不屌"},{"pid":"1ee1df533320ab6ff90a8813342cedafd3d705c0","tid":850312,"uid":76105,"like":78,"dislike":4,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"吉野家屌打大家樂大快活啦！"},{"pid":"604311c1407025e549cf24c7181a5a3c9f61e329","tid":850312,"uid":167437,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1ee1df533320ab6ff90a8813342cedafd3d705c0","tid":850312,"uid":76105,"like":78,"dislike":4,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"吉野家屌打大家樂大快活啦！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:30:05.000Z","msg":"附近冇 唔係一早屌左"},{"pid":"a522e38d9694c86b601d3058e6b9403286289301","tid":850312,"uid":95082,"like":9,"dislike":27,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:31:13.000Z","msg":"火你老母鍋"},{"pid":"aa24ad5a5bef9a2e5afb855f8fa7c89e29591dab","tid":850312,"uid":89402,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"1ee1df533320ab6ff90a8813342cedafd3d705c0","tid":850312,"uid":76105,"like":78,"dislike":4,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"吉野家屌打大家樂大快活啦！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"以上呢幾間都可以收皮<br />\n打邊爐一定去酒樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7bbfa27457fdc9cbc11d859fb83cd7c0714a39","tid":850312,"uid":1139,"like"